      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AWESOME RETURN (2) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 1.3 lengths second (17.44) over 300m at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Top prospect. KIARNI BOLT (1) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 300m behind Sacrifice (18.35) in a Grade 3/4. Was a winner the start prior. Key player if finds best. SHE'S SILKY (8) was a last-start winner from the inside at this track and distance (17.44) after charging straight to the lead, scoring by 3.5 lengths. Should be in this for a long way. WEEKEND SCOTCH (4) picked up a cheque over this course and distance most recently - in the mix again.",
